name: UseScaffold Free Demo - Figma Prototyping Library
description:
Scaffold is a Premium Figma Prototyping and Animation Library made by Jason Crabtree to drastically speed up your Figma prototyping workflow.


This free demo contains 7 of the 285 available prototype templates in the full Scaffold library.


Purchase the full 285 prototype premium file at https://usescaffold.com for $29


Save time building complex prototypes like Flyout Hover Menus, Shopping Carts, Payment Authentications, Loading States, Mobile Navigations, Overlays, Pop-overs, interactive links, buttons, and many more.


Learn more at https://usescaffold.com, or contact me on twitter at @jasontcrabtree
